data.description: Spectacular South Toledo Home situated on wooded lot brought into the New Century with all the updates! Fantastic Open Concept. Loads of room to roam. New concrete stamped driveway, Newer entry doors, Newer garage door, Updated kitchen w/island & pantry, Updated baths! Everything has been done! Lower level office could be 4th bedroom. Two wood burn fireplaces. Walkout to rear yard with a ravine view of SwanCreek MetroPark. Stove and dryer are electric but gas lines present!
